<s> This is the wrong forum for that question -- www-dom is really for discussion of the DOM itself rather than of parsers -- but as I understand it most new development goes into the Apache version, which thus always has the latest fixes ... and the latest bugs.  </s>
<s> The IBM-labelled versions (XML4C/XML4J) are released less frequently, have been tested a bit more thoroughly, and include some code that the Apache versions don't (compatbility libraries for folks using the older IBM interfaces, improved internationalization support, that sort of thing).  </s>
