<s> The linkage of XSLT to DOM is, indeed, pretty vague.  </s>
<s> Some XSLT processors accept DOMs as input or produce DOMs as output, some may expose their internal models as DOMs for folks writing "extensions", and some may use the DOM as their internal model (not that anyone could ever tell from outside)... but that's about as far as it goes.  </s>
